00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.500 line:80% position:20% align:start
The system allows you to filter the posts
you are looking for using keywords.

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:11.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
Click the magnifying glass icon in the
bottom menu to display the search bar.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.500 line:80% position:20% align:start
When typing a term, like "john", the feed
updates to show only related posts.

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:22.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
You can search by username or by
specific content within the messages.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:27.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
Clear the text to reset the feed
or enter a new custom search.